text: Neo Jie Shi (; born May 20, 1985) is a Singaporean marathon runner. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's marathon, in which she placed 131st. ==References== == External links == * * * * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Singaporean female marathon runners Category:Singaporean female athletes Category:Olympic athletes of Singapore Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
